<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>About Me</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-image: url("img/servicesbackground.jpeg");
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: #070707;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .profile {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .profile-img {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .profile-img img {
      width: 300px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .profile-details {
      flex: 2;
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 40px;
    }

    .profile-details p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .resume-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .resume-link:hover {
      background-color: #e9e9e9;
    }

    .go-back-link {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #080808;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .go-back-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Me</h2>

    <div class="profile">
      <div class="profile-details">
        <p>Name: Riya Sara Joy</p>
        <p>Hello,</p>
        <p>I am Riya Sara Joy from Kerala, India. Currently, I am pursuing a Software Engineering Advanced Diploma at Centennial College Progress Campus. I have a strong passion for travel and exploring new places. My main goal is to secure a position in a good company and contribute my skills and knowledge to meaningful projects. Alongside my career aspirations, I also have a deep passion for teaching and inspiring others. I am excited about the opportunities ahead and look forward to making a positive impact in the software industry.</p>
        <a href="/pdf/resume.pdf" class="resume-link">View Resume</a>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-img">
        <img src="/img/profile.jpg" alt="Profile Picture">
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="go-back-link">Go Back</a>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2023 Your Portfolio. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
